<item>
            <title>[LU-17273] Update GSS context init to support IPv6</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17273</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To support IPv6 NIDs in GSS context init, we would need to change the &lt;tt&gt;nid&lt;/tt&gt; field of &lt;tt&gt;struct svc_nego_data&lt;/tt&gt; to &lt;tt&gt;struct lnet_nid&lt;/tt&gt;, and also the &lt;tt&gt;si_nid4&lt;/tt&gt; field in &lt;tt&gt;struct gss_rsi&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
And then modify how &lt;tt&gt;(struct svc_nego_data *)-&amp;gt;nid&lt;/tt&gt; is handled in userspace for the various security mechanisms (krb5, ssk).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
